<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - RecipeApp</title>
       <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="./images/appLogo/fav.png">
       <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/header.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Reset and General Styling */
        body, h1, p, ul, li, a {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            list-style: none;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        /* General body styling */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #fff;
            background-color: #121212;
            margin-top: 70px;
        }

       

       

        

        /* Container styling */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px;
            
        }

        .profile-container {
            background-color: black;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            
        }

        .profile-container h2 {
            color: #32cd32;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .profile-container p {
            color: white;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #32cd32;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #28a745;
        }

        /* Media Queries for Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 1rem;
            }

            .profile-container h2 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .profile-container p {
                font-size: 16px;
                color: white;
                text-align: justify;
            }
        }
        header img{
            height: 50px;
           
            position: relative;
        
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <%- include("./header") %>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="profile-container">
            <h2>About RecipeApp</h2>
            <p>
                Welcome to RecipeApp, your go-to platform for discovering, sharing, and creating amazing recipes from around the world. 
                Our community is made up of passionate home cooks, professional chefs, and food lovers alike. Whether you're looking for
                new culinary inspiration or want to showcase your favorite dishes, RecipeApp has everything you need!
            </p>
            <p>
                With our easy-to-use interface and personalized recommendations, you can easily find the perfect recipes that suit your tastes. 
                Join us today and start your culinary journey!
            </p>
            <a href="/home/recipe" class="cta-button">Start Exploring</a>
        </div>
    </div>

   
</body>
</html>
